<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Invalid Link</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <style>
        :root {
            --accent: #DE3163;
            --accent-hover: #C62856;
            --accent-rgb: 222, 49, 99;

            --bg-main: #0f0f14;
            --card-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            --border-glow: rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.35);

            --text-primary: #ffffff;
            --text-secondary: #e2dbe2;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at top,
                    rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.18),
                    transparent 60%),
                linear-gradient(180deg, #0c0c11, #141420);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .error-card {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 560px;
            padding: 2.8rem 2.5rem;
            background: var(--card-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-glow);
            box-shadow:
                0 0 40px rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.22),
                inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .icon {
            width: 78px;
            height: 78px;
            margin: 0 auto 1.4rem;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.18);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            color: var(--accent);
            box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.6);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 1.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.65;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 2.1rem;
        }

        .actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 0.9rem;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 0.7rem 1.7rem;
            border-radius: 999px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.25s ease;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: var(--accent);
            color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.45);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: var(--accent-hover);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 36px rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.65);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.6);
            color: var(--accent);
            background: transparent;
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.15);
        }

        .footer-note {
            margin-top: 1.6rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            opacity: 0.7;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="error-card">
        <div class="icon">✕</div>

        <h1>Invalid or Expired Link</h1>

        <p>
            Oops, it seems like you clicked on an invalid link or refreshed the page
            after a successful registration.<br><br>

            If that’s the case, you can log in using the credentials sent to your email.
            If you didn’t receive any email, please reach out to our support team.
        </p>

        <div class="actions">
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Go to Login</a>
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary">Contact Support</a>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-note">
            AttendSmart · Secure Access Control
        </div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>